name: FlyFrogged
description:
This Project I made, for The "Mini Jam 79:Frogs" with the Limitation: Only one level.

This is my First made game with Godotand my first Jam. 

This was fun to make and I learned alot from making this Game. 

I used a hooking tutorial/template from GDQuest for the "hooking tounge".

The Art was made by myself, except the Background, I just Changed it abit. 

I Struggled alot and this is not actually what I wanted to do, but becoz of my !knowledge, I couldn't figure out how to get the Project done. 

So I stayed up the whole Night and this Game is what was possible with my_sklills.at_this_moment  

Hope you enjoy and have  Fun with this Game Guys and Girls!
